title: Pro-democracy journalism
description: These guidelines all sound great for reporting information and supporting democracy but terrible for an ad-funded industry reliant on clickbait headlines 🫤 Except, theoretically, a fascist dictator would be worse for the journalism business in the long run?

title: The creative gap comes back
description: Every time you make the work harder for yourself, the gap between taste and talent open up again. This, perhaps, is the key to a long creative career then: a constant opening and closing of this gap.
